{"tid":465078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷赴英舉報梁振英涉貪","createTime":"2017-11-11T07:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T03:39:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fb109e3a7eb8a67a1dd401f33951e7284ddbffb8","tid":465078,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171111/20210889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F20210889&d=CeERpCKrFVwiV386tkw2u4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=fa5653f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F20210889&h=80e70119\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171111/20210889</a><br />\n<br />\n林卓廷赴英舉報梁振英涉貪<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171111/large/11la6p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F11la6p02.jpg&h=f0449a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林卓廷要求英國NCA徹查梁振英UGL事件。林卓廷提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前特首梁振英涉嫌收取澳洲企業UGL 400萬英鎊事件，發生至今3年仍受關注。民主黨立法會議員林卓廷周五抵英，前往英國執法機構國家打擊犯罪調查局（NCA）舉報梁涉嫌貪污及逃稅。林帶同相關文件與局方官員會面，對話逾1.5小時，並指會面後完全感受對方誠意，會緊密聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n向NCA提文件要求徹查<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷周五到埗後，於英國時間早上10時，與NCA轄下的International corruption unit官員舉報梁，並向NCA Director General Lynne Owens女士提交信件，至11時多離開。他會面後接受訪問時表示，因保密原則未能公開雙方討論的具體內容，但他指會面時先向對方詳細講解事件背景，然後提交相關文件，如2011年12月2日UGL向梁發出協議書，就UGL收購戴德梁行訂定協議內容，披露梁收取的款項、梁事後回應，及媒體報道等。 <br />\n<br />\n他稱局方官員曾數度提問，作深入了解，完全感受到對方誠意，因梁是英國上市公司戴德梁行董事之一，希望NCA能深入調查，稍後會提交更多資料予局方，現階段未確實下次會面時間。 他坦言，事件發生至今3年，UGL調查進度「拖得太耐」，認為立法會建制派一直反對調查案件，梁亦不配合，廉署的刑事調查進展未明，故希望香港及英國都可盡早調查，讓公眾釋疑。 <br />\n<br />\n同日英國時間下午，林會與英國外交部代表Warren Leigh會面，討論香港實施一國兩制下所面對的法治及人權等問題。<br />\n<br />\n■特約記者彭碧珊英國報道"},{"pid":"1e705b12a3f1678a31002767730fd9b3509d451e","tid":465078,"uid":102132,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed1831b543a9dfdaf1b66a52dd09e4b656a6e6de","tid":465078,"uid":51904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:41:35.000Z","msg":"林卓廷都飛埋去英國<br />\nKK架飛機仲未起飛去英國搞何君堯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f7a8075487dd370aace7d3bde439ee8c465436","tid":465078,"uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T07:43:56.000Z","msg":"...台都落左先去搞<br />\n係都搞何君堯"},{"pid":"2535e777665b90cad31b7f2b522a8d15b9144fa7","tid":465078,"uid":15309,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>...台都落左先去搞<br />\n係都搞何君堯</blockquote><br />\n兩個都要搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b33bf67ddda28cb038e0f4f39f34157258245c5","tid":465078,"uid":53172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>...台都落左先去搞<br />\n係都搞何君堯</blockquote><br />\n兩個都要搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7700807bf697dc81a1df99759b1d640b3e32c4a3","tid":465078,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>...台都落左先去搞<br />\n係都搞何君堯</blockquote><br />\n兩個都要搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw做實事就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951dce02a283299c36f08d78b375151b1fccd8c1","tid":465078,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face